@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Create and Connect Instance
POST {{baseUrl}}/create-and-connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instanceName": "gustavo"
}

### Check Connection Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/connection-status/gustavo

### Logout Instance
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/logout/gustavo

### Restart Instance
POST {{baseUrl}}/restart/gustavo

### Send Messages
POST {{baseUrl}}/instances/send-messages/testInstance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contacts": [
    {
      "number": "5511999999999",
      "name": "John Doe"
    },
    {
      "number": "5511888888888",
      "name": "Jane Smith"
    }
  ],
  "messages": [
    "Hello @name, how are you?",
    "Don't forget our meeting, @name!"
  ],
  "delay": 10
}

### Upload CSV and Send Messages
POST {{baseUrl}}/instances/upload-csv-and-send/testInstance
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

